title: Princess in Love (1996)
description:
Princess in Love (1996)

TV Movie  -  94 min  -  Drama  -  1996

She was the fairytale bride blessed with movie star looks, adored by the nation, but trapped in a loveless marriage to the heir to England's throne. He was the dashing young cavalry officer who turned her head and stole her heart, before finally being branded 'a love rat'.
Based on Anna Pasternak's book, 'Princess In Love' reveals the truth behind the clandestine affair that rocked the British monarchy, touched the lives of millions and changed the course of history forever...
